1.0.1.name: wordpress/flm-golf-booking
1.0.1.description:
This plug-in allows a golf course to accept bookings for course, lessons and function rooms from either visitors or members. The plug-in is provided by the makers of the golf booking system bookitee and this can be seen at http://www.bookitee.com.

Ideal for sporting entrepreneurs to implement in sporting clubs.

To view a fresh install of FLM Golf Booking - http://www.bookitime.com/flm-golf-club-booking-page/

Features Include

  • Accept bookings from visitors
  • Accept bookings from members
  • Multiple courses can be booked
  • Each different course can have different timeslot gaps
  • Each course can have different visitor prices
  • Multi-Time zone and Multi currency
  • Used in operational golf clubs, so you can trust that the software is robust
  • E-mail conf
